            "abstractNote": "Bat diversity within Pantanos de Centla Biosphere Reserve (RBPC) is little known. Increasing the understanding and knowledge of this mammal group is important for conservation actions. Because of this, a literature search through national and international databases was conducted. Bat assemblage at RBPC is composed of 36 species, 25 genera, and ﬁve families. Three species are listed in the NOM-059-SEMARNAT-2010. This information provides a baseline for decision-making to maintain and conserve bats in the Biosphere Reserve of the Pantanos de Centla.",
